These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
City: hannover, san-francisco, miami, edinburgh
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, apricot, ebony
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, sprite, milk
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the person who likes orange is the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who likes orange is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City         | hannover  | edinburgh  | san-francisco | miami |
| Color           | orange | turquise | ebony  | apricot  |
| Beverage   | milk       | sprite      | tea | juice      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

