.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, epic, horror, time-travel
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, woodworking, dancing, board-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend, baccarat, aristoff
1. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the bongani-smoker##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Movie-Genre          | time-travel     | epic       | horror   | musical   |
| Hobby   | dancing      | woodworking       | board-games     | sudoku    |
| Cigar         | baccarat | aristoff | bongani | blend |

