.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, whist, go
City: hamburg, paris, london, colone
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, british, turkish
 1. the person drinking tea is the turkish##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
 4. the british is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the turkish##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Game           | mah-jongg   | whist | poker   | go |
| City   | hamburg     | paris    | colone | london        |
| Nationality           | british         | brazilian  | turkish       | pakistani         |

