.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
City: san-francisco, venice, miami, edinburgh
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, electronic, funk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, volleyball, rugby
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, brown, blue
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes brown is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| City           | venice   | san-francisco  | edinburgh | miami |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Sport   | volleyball       | rugby    | sailing     | climbing  |
| Color           | fuchsia     | brown | blue     | light-blue         |

