.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, guinea-pig, turtle, goat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, romance, spy, superhero
House: farmhouse, cottage, craftsman, ranch-style
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, march, october
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the craftsman house##1
7. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Pet           | pony  | turtle    | guinea-pig | goat |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | romance    | drama         | superhero    |
| House   | cottage   | farmhouse     | craftsman          | ranch-style      |
| Birthday         | february | december | october      | march      |

