.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, poker, whist
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, alhambra, oliveros, dunhill
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, august, may
 1. the person playing poker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person playing chess is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the bolivar-smoker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing chess##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | chess  | whist | poker     | bridge |
| Cigar           | oliveros  | dunhill      | bolivar | alhambra    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Birthday           | august   | may       | april       | december      |

