 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the farmhouse house##1
 8. the mechanic is on the far left##1
 9. the mechanic is on the left of the photographer##1
10. the cottage house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
