4. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the accountant is on the left of the townhouse house##1
6. the social-worker is the futuristic house##1
7. the teacher is the owner of the frog##1
8. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
9. the person eating raspberry is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
