4 different pets are kept: fish, goldfish, bird, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, sailing, volleyball
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who growsrose##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
8. the person who growsdaisy is the person traveling to liverpool##1
9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| City      | edinburgh     | liverpool           | new-york    | hamburg    |
| Flower         | amaryllis  | daisy | daffodil  | rose |
| Pet   | bird     | fish     | goldfish | rabbit   |
