4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the brazilian##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
6. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing poker##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
9. the italian is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | water | hot-chocolate     | tea       | milk |
| Cigar   | oliveros      | aristoff      | vegafina     | fonseca   |
| Nationality   | italian   | brazilian | indonesian | malaysian |
| Game     | domino    | poker       | snooker    | whist     |

